data.description: Here is your chance to own a beautifully updated oasis in the highly desirable Palm Harbor section of Palm Coast! The open floorpan boasts plenty of space for entertaining with beautiful salt water canal views from all around. This home further features tile and laminate flooring throughout and two newly remodeled bathrooms that boast granite countertops, new cabinetry and finished showers. The owners also added a nice indoor mudroom style laundry area that is perfect for kids and dogs. Moving to the outside, the covered boat house features a newer boat lift and roof. The pool deck and patio are perfect for those evening dips in the pool and enjoying a perfect sunrise in the morning. The property is fully fenced and also has a deck with next to the boat dock. The front of the home features a newer paver half moon driveway with plenty of parking for the whole family. Other notable features include plush landscaping and a security system with multiple exterior cameras and a monitoring station inside the home. Bring your buyers and a boat.......Schedule a showing today!
